import{_ as t,c as o,b as a,o as n}from"./chunks/framework.Bh4f_7Kc.js";const c=JSON.parse('{"title":"","description":"","frontmatter":{},"headers":[],"relativePath":"guide/Mark Zuckerberg.md","filePath":"guide/Mark Zuckerberg.md"}'),i={name:"guide/Mark Zuckerberg.md"};function s(r,e,p,h,l,d){return n(),o("div",null,e[0]||(e[0]=[a("<p>I think the best company is not the one that creates and develops itself, but the one that makes great changes in your heart.</p><p>---002---</p><p>We are not born with this kind of beautiful feeling in our hearts. Through constant efforts and practice, we will naturally be able to see more of the good things in the world.</p><p>---003---</p><p>To tell others simply: we don&#39;t create services to make money; we make money to provide better services. We are good at this because this is the attitude of all good people.</p><p>---004---</p><p>I want to live my life as realistically and simply as possible, so you don&#39;t have to spend too much time making decisions for her.</p><p>---005---</p><p>After I opened the way, I asked myself a question: Am I doing the best I can do now? Only when I got a positive answer, I felt comfortable and felt that my energy was not wasted.</p><p>---006---</p><p>If you are jealous of others, it may be because you are not as good as others, but because you are jealous of others.</p><p>---007---</p><p>But once we get to Shao, we can&#39;t think clearly. Only when we get to Shao, we will know more and more clearly. &quot;</p><p>---008---</p><p>Stand up and think big. Surround yourself with great people, build great friendships, and make friends you can trust. These friendships, these relationships that support you, are the key to success. No one can accomplish great things alone, but they do it with friends. It&#39;s partners, it&#39;s partners who create greatness together. Pay attention to making friends, and have fun while you&#39;re at it.</p><p>---009---</p><p>I made a lot of stupid mistakes when I was just a kid at university, and I don&#39;t want to make excuses for them. Some of the accusations against me are fake, and some are made up. I was only 19 when I launched Facebook, and a lot of things happened that were not true. We went from a server for the university to a social network with 1 billion people using it.</p><p>---010---</p><p>I mean, students are likely to tell others to open their eyes and talk, right? We only have 6 years to sit in front of the computer and write code.</p><p>---011---</p><p>Done is better than perfect.</p><p>What&#39;s more important is to achieve perfection and to stand up for the best.</p><p>---012---</p><p>Our mission is to get more people to see the good things in the world, to connect more people. By sharing the good things in the world, people can communicate with the people they want to connect with, and we can see this in the pictures and small worlds.</p><p>---013---</p><p>No way, we can&#39;t forget that Facebook has been a controversial company in the past. This is not the first time we have experienced ups and downs.</p><p>---014---</p><p>My colleagues and I have all bought this book. I hope that you can read it more to understand the social customs in China.</p><p>---015---</p><p>To put it simply: we don&#39;t make money by developing services, we make money in order to provide better services and develop them more perfectly. And you can&#39;t think of this as a good way for others to develop in the future.</p><p>---016---</p><p>I want to tell you a secret: we don&#39;t know how many good talents there are when we first find them, and our ideas will not be fully formed when we first find them. Only when your mind becomes clearer as you work, you just need to stand up and think of yourself as a good talent.</p><p>---017---</p><p>The idea of ​​a social graph is that if you map out the connections between people, you have a social graph, which is what Facebook is trying to do. Once you have that, you can start building services on top of it, turn it into more platforms, build games, etc. Many people think that social graphs are something we own or control, but in reality they are not.</p><p>---018---</p><p>First, it is not enough for us as millennials to simply find our personal Shao Zi’s or mission;</p><p>Second, the challenge facing our generation in particular is to stand up and create a path for the public. This is the key to the true happiness of students and the only way for us to maintain our social integrity.</p><p>The first thing that happened was that we were the first to stand up and build a connection on our own, and then we got to know the local community.</p><p>---019---</p><p>If the ones you love are all good, you have the ability to stand together in adversity.</p><p>---020---</p><p>Dear Max,</p><p>Your mother and I don&#39;t yet have the words to describe the hope you give us for the future. Your new life is full of promise, and we hope you will be happy and healthy so you can explor it fully. You&#39;ve already given us a reason to reflect on the world we hope you live in.</p><p>---021---</p><p>When the eyes open, human-machine, virtual reality, and artificial intelligence are all indispensable.</p><p>---022---</p><p>The greatest virtue of an investor is patience.</p>",47)]))}const y=t(i,[["render",s]]);export{c as __pageData,y as default};
